-- MOVES-Principal names Thomas Cheong VP of North Asia for Principal International
-- By Shivam Srivastava in Bengaluru
-- Tue Dec 23, 2014 04:06AM EST
-- None



Dec 23 (Reuters) - Investment management company Principal Financial Group <PFG.N> appointed Thomas Cheong as vice president of North Asia for Principal International.

Cheong will join in early January from Manulife Asset Management in Taiwan where he was CEO and executive director. He will report to Rex Auyeung, president, Principal International (Asia). [ID:nBw4pHzZ9a] Cheong will oversee Principal International operations and relationships in mainland China and Hong Kong.